author: Hugh Jeffreys
description:
The fallout from the 3G shutdown continues, even more than a year on. 70 models have just been identified as unable to call 000. 
11 Models are to be blocked this month with the future of the remaining 59 models uncertain. How many other models out there have gone un-noticed. 

Check your phone at isthisphoneblocked.net.au

Australia's 3G shutdown playlist: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcIRTWL3XaQ2RWqiSP81ry_Sm2JFjZhti
title: Australia Just Banned These Samsung Galaxy Phones
